CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 23, 1966, pg. 11B, reads: "Scientists All - Participants in Northview Heights Elementary School's first Science O Rama are pictured here during the last day of their three day science fair. From left to right, first row - Kathleen Baker, Stephanie Mowery, Deborah Fairbanks, Patricia Jackson, Sarah Heagy, Mary Grace Eckhardt, Veronica Cappo, Sharon Alexander, Deborah Novak.  Second row - Frank Reynolds, Geneva Adams, Elaine Simon, Anthony Capo, James Walton, Larry Moneck, Charles Hartle, Charlotte Kurtz, Deborah Wailersbacher.  Last row - Mary Waller, Albert Chamberlain, Rodney Arthur, Thomas Plett, Albert Davenport, Jerry Knight, Charles Leivis, James Howard."
TitMainTitle: Ten children posed with trophy at Northview Heights Elementary School Science O Rama
